150	    /// This returns an array of the labels that are unused given an argument
151	    /// list.
152	    /// The unused labels are in the order they are expected to be passed in
153	    /// to a call using those.
154	    ///
155	    /// ## Examples
156	    ///
157	    /// ```gleam
